  { q: 'Can Jobber handle the same volume as ServiceTitan?', a: 'Jobber can handle up to 500 jobs per month efficiently on their Core plan and 2,000+ jobs on Connect and Grow plans. ServiceTitan is built for unlimited job volume but the complexity may be overkill for companies under 1,000 monthly jobs.' },
  { q: 'Which platform is easier to implement for a growing HVAC company?', a: 'Jobber takes 1-2 weeks to fully implement with minimal training required. ServiceTitan requires 4-12 weeks for full implementation plus extensive training sessions. Most HVAC companies with under 25 employees find Jobber significantly easier to adopt.' },
  { q: 'Does ServiceTitan justify its higher cost for mid-sized HVAC companies?', a: 'ServiceTitan justifies its cost for companies with 50+ employees, complex inventory needs, or multiple locations. For companies with 10-25 employees doing residential and light commercial work, Jobber typically provides better ROI with 95% of needed features at 10% of the cost.' },
