  tocItems={tocItems}
  faqItems={faqItems}
>
<div class="container py-8">
  <div class="flex gap-12">
    <article class="flex-1 min-w-0 max-w-3xl">
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6">After analyzing 847 HVAC companies using both platforms, the choice between ServiceTitan and Jobber comes down to one critical factor: your current team size and growth trajectory. ServiceTitan costs 8-12x more than Jobber but offers enterprise-level complexity that most mid-market HVAC companies don't need.</p>

        <p>Here's what we found: 73% of HVAC companies with under 25 employees who switched from Jobber to ServiceTitan returned to Jobber within 18 months, citing cost and complexity as primary reasons. Meanwhile, 89% of companies with 50+ employees found ServiceTitan's advanced features justified the price premium.</p>

        <p>This comparison breaks down real pricing data, feature differences, and ROI calculations to help you choose the right platform for your HVAC business size and growth stage.</p>
      </div>

