      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p><strong>Hidden Costs to Consider:</strong></p>
        
        <p><strong>ServiceTitan Additional Fees:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Implementation: $5,000-25,000 depending on complexity</li>
          <li>Data migration: $3,000-15,000 from existing systems</li>
          <li>Training: $2,000-8,000 for comprehensive team training</li>
          <li>Custom integrations: $1,500-5,000 per integration</li>
          <li>Advanced reporting modules: $200-500/month additional</li>
        </ul>

