          <li>Data migration: $0-500 for complex transfers</li>
          <li>Training: $0 (free webinars and resources)</li>
          <li>Most integrations: $0-50/month</li>
        </ul>

        <p>For a 15-person HVAC team, the first-year cost difference typically ranges from $12,000-18,000, with ongoing annual savings of $8,000-12,000 by choosing Jobber over ServiceTitan.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 id="feature-comparison" class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Feature-by-Feature Comparison</h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
        <table class="w-full border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr style="background: #1B4F72; color: white;">
              <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Feature Category</th>
              <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Jobber</th>
              <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd;">ServiceTitan</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr style="background: #f8f9fa;">
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Job Scheduling</strong></td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Drag-and-drop scheduler, route optimization for 500+ jobs/month</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Advanced scheduling with capacity planning, unlimited job volume</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Customer Management</strong></td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Contact management, service history, 2-way texting</td>
