              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Advanced pricing matrices, payment plans, revenue recognition</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Inventory Management</strong></td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Basic inventory tracking, purchase orders</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Multi-location inventory, automated reordering, vendor management</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background: #f8f9fa;">
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Mobile App</strong></td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Full-featured mobile app, works offline</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Enterprise mobile app with advanced forms and workflows</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Reporting</strong></td>
